Installation notes for aEncoder for linux

1) Your must have installed packages:
	- mencoder with libfaac support
	- tk8.5
	- tcl8.5
	- gpac >= 0.4.4

In debian-like systems you can install it by simple command:
	aptitude install tcl8.5 tk8.5 gpac mencoder

NOTE: Debian users have this packes in debian-multimedia repository

2) Just run install.sh. It check binaries and create aEncoder start script

3) Profit!
